{{Libertarianism}}

'''溫蒂·莫艾洛依'''（{{Lang|en|Wendy McElroy}}'''；'''{{BD|1951年|}}是[[加拿大|加拿大]]的[[個人無政府主義|個人無政府主義]]者和[[个人主义|個人]][[女性主義|女性主義]]者。她的著作包括了對於懲罰[[性骚扰|性骚扰]]的法律條文的嚴厲批評<ref>{{Cite web|title=Abolish Anti-Discrimination Laws|url=https://www.lewrockwell.com/2006/01/wendy-mcelroy/abolish-anti-discrimination-laws/|access-date=2021-10-14|work=LewRockwell|language=en|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102054215/https://www.lewrockwell.com/2006/01/wendy-mcelroy/abolish-anti-discrimination-laws/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、尤其與大學校園性騷擾政策有關的各種議題，她認為那些政策和法律條文是相當模糊兩可的。她也替[[色情|色情]]產業的正當性辯護，反對政府禁止這些活動。並且批評其他女性主義流派的反色情運動<ref>{{Cite web|title=You Are What You Read?|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061025023931/http://www.lewrockwell.com/mcelroy/mcelroy14.html|access-date=2021-10-14|date=2006-10-25|work=web.archive.org}}</ref>。

莫艾洛依也是目前在世的知名[[無政府資本主義|無政府資本主義]]者之一。她在'''ifeminists.com'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=News - ifeminists.com|url=http://www.ifeminists.net/e107_plugins/enews/enews.php|access-date=2021-10-14|work=www.ifeminists.net|archive-date=2021-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211028143204/http://www.ifeminists.net/e107_plugins/enews/enews.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[福斯新聞頻道|福斯新聞]]網站<ref>{{Cite web|title=Opinion - FOXNews.com|url=https://www.foxnews.com/column_archive/0,2976,16,00.html|access-date=2021-10-14|work=www.foxnews.com|archive-date=2021-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211028191353/https://www.foxnews.com/column_archive/0,2976,16,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>都有著定期的專欄。[[File:Wendy_McElroy_16_September_2006_AM_2.jpg|thumb]]
==著作==
{{Portal|女权主义}}
* ''National Identification Systems: Essays in Opposition'', by Carl Watner, Wendy McElroy, January 1, 2004 ISBN 0-7864-1595-9
*''Debates of Liberty: An Overview of Individualist Anarchism, 1881-1908'', February 1, 2003 ISBN 0-7391-0473-X
*''Liberty for Women: Freedom and Feminism in the Twenty-First Century'', May 1, 2002 ISBN 1-56663-435-0
*''Sexual Correctness: The Gender-Feminist Attack on Women'', June 2001
*''Dissenting Electorate: Those Who Refuse to Vote and the Legitimacy of Their Opposition'' by Carl Watner, Wendy McElroy, January 1, 2001
*''Individualist Feminism of the Nineteenth Century: Collected Writings and Biographical Profiles'', January 1, 2001
*''Queen Silver : The Godless Girl'' (Women's Studies (Amherst, N.Y.) by Wendy McElroy, Queen Selections Silver, December 1, 1999
*''Freedom, Feminism, and the State'' by Wendy McElroy, Lewis Perry, February 1, 1999
*''The Reasonable Woman: A Guide to Intellectual Survival'', April 1, 1998
*''XXX: A Women's Right to Pornography'' by Wendy McElroy, Prelude Pr, 1995, ISBN 0-312-13626-9
*''Liberty, 1881-1908: A Comprehensive Index'', January 1982

